{"tid":1166541,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個前度好嘅地方","createTime":"2019-05-22T13:17:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T19:45:43.000Z","uid":110808,"like":30,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e498c171d65ec97168af09d8076ee22b50c58e1b","tid":1166541,"uid":110808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T13:17:01.000Z","msg":"我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中學時期大家起身都趕住返學，但都會每日morning call我，我懶床想訓多10分鐘佢又真係會睇住時間再call過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一齊幾年每次出街都會送返屋企，真係有事都會傾住電話陪住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中學生冇錢，但間唔中會買我鐘意嘅零食俾驚喜我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來當分開得夠耐，就會連當初分開嘅原因都唔記得，淨係記得對方好嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (帽另計)<br />\n<br />\n利伸: 散左好幾年 但啲咁青春嘅回憶應該會記一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e256a9c23a8dd215312749d09c4e049af4e2445","tid":1166541,"uid":251861,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T14:04:18.000Z","msg":"一齊陪做癲野，個陣明明仲係學生，一放學就翻工，出糧就用曬黎買野送俾我，帶我周圍食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去到邊都想要接我送我翻屋企，有事第一個出黎保護我。。可惜已經係前度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"497644e94de25381cd52a8fb8ac91ae90f605e22","tid":1166541,"uid":182134,"like":19,"dislike":3,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T14:24:43.000Z","msg":"發埋啲On9 Post有乜意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n懷念前度好都唔知係開心好定傷心好"},{"pid":"6ef5d2f863a1ff15cf1daf71d73021f6cb601126","tid":1166541,"uid":70374,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T14:27:13.000Z","msg":"着住旗袍校服比我中出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e483f5f5de03aca4a7816ed956a516f29701d8e3","tid":1166541,"uid":204808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,